+ What this is:

> This theme was developed by [[*user MalyceGraves]] to be used in conjunction with tales and SCP articles written in and for the Canon  [[[memoria-adytum|In Memoria, Adytum]]]. 
> 
> This theme is licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0


++ Additionally 
This is a Black Highlighter + BHL Collapsible Sidebar based theme. You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. [[[theme:black-highlighter|To learn more go here.]]]

